DATA PROCESSING AND PRIVACY

This software processes enterprise data and may handle sensitive information. 
Users are responsible for:

1. Ensuring compliance with applicable data protection regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
2. Implementing appropriate data security measures
3. Obtaining necessary consents for data processing
4. Maintaining audit trails and data lineage
5. Implementing data retention and deletion policies
6. Ensuring proper data classification and handling

