CHANGELOG

Version 1.0.0 (2026-01-29)
- Initial release of Azure Synapse Analytics Data Platform
- Unified analytics workspace with SQL and Spark compute engines
- Advanced machine learning integration with Azure ML and MLflow
- Comprehensive data warehousing with dedicated SQL pools and serverless SQL
- Production-ready infrastructure templates (Bicep and Terraform)
- Complete data pipeline orchestration and monitoring
- Enterprise-grade security and compliance features
- Medallion architecture implementation (Bronze, Silver, Gold)
- Real-time and batch processing capabilities

