================================================================================

DATA ARCHITECTURE PATTERNS

This platform implements several industry-standard data architecture patterns:

1. **Medallion Architecture**: Bronze (raw), Silver (processed), Gold (curated)
2. **Modern Data Warehouse**: Combining data lake and data warehouse capabilities
3. **Lambda Architecture**: Supporting both batch and real-time processing
4. **Data Mesh**: Enabling domain-driven data ownership and governance
5. **Lakehouse**: Unified analytics on data lakes with ACID transactions

================================================================================

BEST PRACTICES

When using this platform, follow these best practices:

1. **Data Governance**: Implement proper data classification and lineage tracking
2. **Security**: Use role-based access control and data masking
3. **Performance**: Optimize data partitioning and query patterns
4. **Cost Management**: Monitor usage and implement auto-pause policies
5. **Monitoring**: Set up comprehensive alerting and logging
6. **Backup**: Implement regular backup and disaster recovery procedures

